{"tid":633232,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"(蝗驚an/Iso) 新舊Game集中討論區(1)","createTime":"2018-04-18T06:43:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-21T05:41:56.000Z","uid":119688,"like":3,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cbdf1ae3c4c8566f312e7a22031ce6ca5659c287","tid":633232,"uid":119688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T06:43:11.000Z","msg":"我知一定有負皮,但連登實有人玩<br />\n但無可否認,有好多熱門既都係炒返黎<br />\n但優點係公司有錢去營運去更新<br />\n什至係用高價直接收購買斷版權<br />\n直頭出得仲多過原創,當然你可以唔接受,但打機求開心<br />\n<br />\n優點係咩?<br />\n人多囉唔怕無人同你玩<br />\n討論區攻略網多<br />\n<br />\n缺點呢?<br />\n網絡ping<br />\n課金麻煩<br />\n<br />\n唔逐隻game開post<br />\n直接統一係哂呢度<br />\n<br />\n有興趣留意大陸game<br />\n最好下載九遊官方app<br />\n好多大型/熱門/最新幾乎都關佢事<br />\n直頭係大陸版既google play <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://a.9game.cn/app/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fa.9game.cn%2Fapp%2F&d=1Q3%2BxJXaAi9Upjup037KZjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=3425354e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://a.9game.cn/app/</a><br />\n<br />\n四月份好game介紹(已公測)(炒人)<br />\n笫五人格(有人開過但沉左落深海)<br />\n玩法鬼捉人 人就解碼開門逃走<br />\n係炒襲game 原版我自己封測早就玩過,覺得陸版呢隻好玩好多"},{"pid":"95ce40af93459cf9dff13356f806b0a6e72e4014","tid":633232,"uid":119688,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T06:44:19.000Z","msg":"屌手快打錯iso<br />\n自膠左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4f127c50c19438d6ab9cb7cbce15fb9c2a47504","tid":633232,"uid":119688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T06:47:37.000Z","msg":"仲有開放mmo<br />\n明日之後<br />\n(暫時未定日期)<br />\n<a href=\"https://survive.163.com/m/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsurvive.163.com%2Fm%2F&d=1Q3%2BxJXaAi9Upjup037KZjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=5126d0cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://survive.163.co